OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775308265
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched in
OL,4,CWoolwich as 14-year-old is shot dead
OL,6,FPolice have launched a murder
OL,7,Finvestigation after a 14-year-old boy
OL,8,Fwas fatally shot in Woolwich.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to reports of a
OL,11,Fshooting at approximately 15:40hrs on
OL,12,FThursday, 2 April on Lord Warwick
OL,13,FStreet.
OL,15,FDespite the efforts of paramedics, the
OL,16,Fboy was sadly pronounced dead at the
OL,17,Fscene. His next-of-kin have been
OL,18,Finformed and are being supported by
OL,19,Fspecialist officers.
