OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775308265
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched in
OL,4,CWoolwich as 14-year-old is shot dead
OL,6,FTwo boys, aged 14 and 16, and an 18-
OL,7,Fyear-old man have been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of murder in connection with
OL,9,Fthe incident.
OL,11,FThey remain in custody.
OL,13,FDetective Chief Inspector Lucie Card,
OL,14,Fwhose team is leading the
OL,15,Finvestigation, said:
OL,17,F"Our thoughts remain with the boy's
OL,18,Ffamily and loved ones.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
