CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1775308265
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched in
OL,4,CWoolwich as 14-year-old is shot dead
OL,6,F"We are aware of the concern that this
OL,7,Fincident will cause the local
OL,8,Fcommunity. We have already made three
OL,9,Farrests and our investigation
OL,10,Fcontinues at pace. An increased police
OL,11,Fpresence remains in the area.
OL,13,F"I would appeal for anyone who was in
OL,14,Fthe area at the time, who has CCTV or
OL,15,Fdash cam footage of the incident or
OL,16,Fhas information that could help my
OL,17,Fofficers to come forward."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@ZO]
